---
title: Spiced Prawns & Broccoli Couscous Bowl with Mayonnaise
description: We are ready to kick off our chermoula prawn dinner with a glowing green bowl of couscous. How do we get that scrumptious glow
you may ask - by adding broccoli and baby spinach to the mix. Perfect for injecting colour, freshness and flavour into your night.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
